        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Sunshine State Act</b></p> <p>This bill amends the Calder Act to provide that the standard time for Florida shall be Coordinated Universal Time retarded by four hours (i.e., Daylight Saving Time for the Eastern time zone). </p>]]></text>
